This paper deals with natural language processing and deep neural networks, which are common topics in the computer science sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of unsupervised learning, which is a common topic in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The use of neural networks and deep learning also suggests that the paper could be relevant to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with text transformation and language processing, which could also make it relevant to the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
